FBIS3-15922 "drsov048_b_94019" FBIS-SOV-94-048 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Mar 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues New Government Appointments Announced PM1003161194 Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI in Russian 10 Mar 94 p 1 PM1003161194 Moscow ROSSIYSKIYE VESTI Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Unattributed report under the "Monitoring" rubric: "Cadres"] [Text] By a directive of Viktor Chernomyrdin, Nikolay Mikheyev has been appointed chairman of the Russian Federation Committee for Water Resources. By a directive of the Russian Federation Government, Aleksandr Samusev has been released from the post of deputy minister of fuel and energy, and has been appointed Russian Federation deputy finance minister.
